description: Season 12 is Mona's Season. She's currently undefeated and she's making her mark. This match was shot live and all the world was able to see Mona handling her business with the rookie. The prize round adds an extra hint of humiliation for the rookie since viewers got to see her lose LIVE. We get to see how hard this was for Joey in round 4 when she continues to fight mona. Mona has to whip Joey into shape AGAIN and put her in her place with some tit destruction
title: Mona Wales whips Rookie Joey Minx into shape
